title: The Only Way Elite Achievers Want To Be Coached, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO270
itunes:title: The Only Way Elite Achievers Want To Be Coached, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO270
description: How do you respond to people who are leading or coaching you? The reality is, your response to guidance & instruction is what is going to determine whether you're an average person or an elite achiever. Average people want to tell the coach or leader HOW to lead them. They care about personality, approach, communication style, & all sorts of other things. But elite achievers only care about one thing. In this episode, I tell you what it is.
